# Android Bugfix Flow

When a bug fix touches Android files, always run this flow before replying:

1. Build debug APK:
   - `cd easyfamily-android && ./gradlew --no-daemon assembleDebug`
2. Reinstall APK to emulator/device:
   - `adb install -r easyfamily-android/app/build/outputs/apk/debug/app-debug.apk`
3. Restart app to foreground:
   - `adb shell am force-stop com.easyfamily`
   - `adb shell am start -n "com.easyfamily/.MainActivity"`

## If any step fails

- Stop and report the exact failed step and key error line.
- Provide the next action taken (or required) to unblock.

## Response requirement

- In the final message, include:
  - Build result
  - Install result
  - Launch result
